Old Man Wulfstrael, who dispatches livestock with his trusty hammer, and their two daughters, Hilda and Editha, who hunt game with their bows. The family generally deals in meat and hides, raising cattle, sheep and pigs, but also tanning and preparing pelts and hides for trade.
